simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Implements the Noop command that demonstrates the MPC task is alive

simplesect.title: Command Verification
simplesect.para:
Successful execution of this command may be verified with the following telemetry:
$sc_$cpu_MPC_CMDACTPCNT - command counter will increment
The #MPC_CMD_INF_EID informational event message will be generated when the command is received

simplesect.title: Error Conditions
simplesect.para:
This command may fail for the following reason(s):
Command packet length not as expected

simplesect.title: Evidence of failure may be found in the following telemetry:

listitem.para: $sc_$cpu_MPC_CMDRJCTCNT - command error counter will increment
The MPC_MSGLEN_ERR_EID error event message will be generated if the command has the wrong length.

simplesect.title: Criticality
simplesect.para: None

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Resets the MPC housekeeping counters

simplesect.title: Command Verification
simplesect.para:
Successful execution of this command may be verified with the following telemetry:
- command counter will be cleared
$sc_$cpu_MPC_CMDRJCTCNT - command error counter will be cleared
The #MPC_CMD_INF_EID debug event message will be generated when the command is executed

simplesect.title: Error Conditions
simplesect.para:
This command may fail for the following reason(s):
Command packet length not as expected

simplesect.title: Evidence of failure may be found in the following telemetry:

listitem.para: $sc_$cpu_MPC_CMDRJCTCNT - command error counter will increment
The MPC_MSGLEN_ERR_EID error event message will be generated if the command has the wrong length.

simplesect.title: Error Conditions
simplesect.para:
This command may fail for the following reason(s):
Command packet length not as expected.
Arguments are invalid or out of bounds.
